Name: fsearch
Version: 0.1.3
Release: alt1

Summary: A fast file search utility for Unix-like systems based on GTK+3
Summary(ru_RU.UTF-8): Утилита для быстрого поиска файлов на основе GTK+3

License: GPL-2.0-only
Group: File tools
Url: http://cboxdoerfer.github.io/fsearch

